description.displayText: I've had the pleasure of knowing Rachel for many years now. Having worked with her both professionally and otherwise, I know how dependable she is. She is timely and caring, and is quite considerate of others' needs. She is a responsible individual who has a longstanding history of working with young children, having worked with them in both a a summer camp setting and abroad. Rachel is a great listener and creative with kids. I emphatically recommend her!
